  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5864046/" class="title-link">解读老子只读此译注本足够</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5864046"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/peterreeves/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1519764-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/peterreeves/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">风萧萧</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-04-12"
      class="main-meta">2013-04-12 17:08:09</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5864046_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  此卷在手，爱不忍释，有一种“觉今是而昨非”的彻悟的感觉，它重构了我对老子的认知，准确正常地理解了老子。一直想写它的书评，推荐给爱读书的人，无奈有了孩子之后，时间变成了碎片，鲁迅说时间像海绵里的水，而我现在的时间就像是石头里的水。不过庆幸终于写完了。         ...

